Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揺れる水面　その深くに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青い宇宙映ってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来…そしてまた散っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}季節覚えている？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私たちは運命紡ぎながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その糸がどこまで続いてくのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}知らないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(ただそこに)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}inspiration　喜びとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}言葉を分かち合うたび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああいつか終わりの日が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう感じさせるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}initialize　その扉を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}開ける時が来るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}綺麗な時を閉じ込めて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}湖に沈めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど私平気だよと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星の便りに綴る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:20.56,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在涟漪的水面深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:24.22,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照映着蔚蓝的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.33,0:22:27.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来又将飘零而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:31.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}唯此季节长存心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:39.44,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我们编织命运之丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:44.70,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却从来都不曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.49,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这丝线将通向何处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.04,0:22:49.42,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs17}(仅仅伫立于此)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:52.61,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}每当我与他人分享
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:56.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灵感乍现时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:00.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就已经隐约察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.84,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终会有结束的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:07.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}重置人生的那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.36,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终有渐渐打开之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}美好时光关入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再慢慢地沉入湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:22.71,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不过我会在星星上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.93,0:23:28.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}写下一句「我没事」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨这种东西  自从飞碟来了后就再没见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能看见  也要等上半个月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学一直在等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从七年前的那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家拜托了  一起参加北美祭吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:04.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\pos(406,270)}「她所相信的东西」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  水坂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要参加北美祭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要做留学的准备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.18,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些摆脱不了的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  待会儿有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok  ok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便就行啦  接下来的就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预算到手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后参加者的名单里  把汐音也写了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是参加北美祭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们五个人一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话跟我说  指的是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年级学生是不强制参加的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么趁人齐一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  户川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是用来做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是贴冰箱上的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急急忙忙把我拉过来  到底是想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是个麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是柚季  提议的是古宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川应该是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是一直很要好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直有种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱因什么的  会不会是点很无聊的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连要做什么都不知道  怎么可能找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是古宫一个人找回来的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星象仪
