Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才要开始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已经很晚了  明天再开始做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学  今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来  明天见
