Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小只啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔  真是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了哟  诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:05:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话来看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北美祭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是特别黄金券
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以给家人或者朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  诺艾尔去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔是飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞碟跑太远的话  会发生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  跟汐音看见流星雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得一定能看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音也可以跟大家一起欢笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托诺艾尔留言的福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.47,0:07:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天冰箱里满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔喜欢吃的东西  都做给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  那蛋包饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿番茄酱画画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似不怎么像？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑太太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个试作机可是花了不少时间和精力做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西真的能映出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得再弄黑一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川做的那个  不是可以用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮了忙  我要去看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  大家也都帮了忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.98,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以运行的话  大家按顺序看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  赶快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我打开开关了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮度完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把电力增大就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大功率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫消防车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  要先切断电源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为我的失败才变成这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  这个你一直带着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天想和大家一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这份感觉真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文台吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  乃乃香叫我们去召唤飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像今天一样  大家都在筹备着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聊着该怎么做  进行着各种尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来  觉得真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上飞碟也出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那飞碟  真的是我们召唤过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但我们在不同的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这里见面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季和凑太是双胞胎兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人性格不相似
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是关系非常亲昵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春的话  她非常非常的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音和妈妈相处得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人一起去看过星星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一起去看这次的流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经约定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔会一直在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果汐音来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能帮我转告她一声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然就要见不到面了  但是我会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会立刻回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候  大家一起去看流星雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  交给诺艾尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该要我自己和她说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会分开什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  你哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么样才能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个教给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.39,0:12:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是汐音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会哼这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香已经去远方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但乃乃香说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很快就会回来的  到时候一起去看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  诺艾尔去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是飞碟跑太远的话  会发生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音要是没有这个  就不能进场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音不想和乃乃香一起去看流星雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔没有清楚地传达给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  诺艾尔已经清楚地传达给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能一起欢笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为乃乃香是一个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香才不是骗子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.98,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香  就快回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一起去看流星雨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还回来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直相信着乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕被信任的人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香按照约定回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错的人是没能自始至终相信乃乃香的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是变了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  乃乃香和大家都完全没有变哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为乃乃香遵守了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次轮到诺艾尔来实现愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音  和乃乃香一起去看流星雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年可以很清楚地看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想上车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此机会  我想问个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜欢  还是讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然做出了这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家帮了很大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能代替流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直没能实现约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经物是人非了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知如此  为何还要等待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…户川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还回来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现和汐音的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但直到和诺艾尔相遇之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的忘记了在这座小镇上所经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚季  小春  凑太也都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的事  完全想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不会再次想起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是…很过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和汐音一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份感情  一直深埋在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时开始就从未改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.62,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是因为  汐音是我最重要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差劲的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能自始至终相信最重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明已经按照约定回来了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对诺艾尔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我想一起去看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和乃乃香再次成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方式可不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫户川汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用星象仪来代替流星雨…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年可以很清楚地看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为诺艾尔是飞碟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音说她今天会来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她说会和我们一起准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确实是我熟悉的乃乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经不能再在一起了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  天体的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
